Ada OPARAJI, Appellant,
v.
CITIBANK, N.A., Respondent. 2018-275 Court of Appeals of New York. Decided May 3, 2018

***1063Motion for leave to appeal dismissed upon the ground that this Court does not have jurisdiction to entertain the motion for leave to appeal from the order of the Appellate Division entered in this action commenced in Civil Court of the City of New York ( NY Const., art VI, § 3 [b][7]; CPLR 5602[a] ).
